          *** Installing the program in WinBoard ***

  download winboard
  http://www.tim-mann.org
  
  open file winboard.ini 
  and add path to prog_dir

...

/firstChessProgramNames={GNUChess
"OBender" /fd=C:\Games\OBender            <---
"GNUChes5 xboard"
}
/secondChessProgramNames={GNUChess
"OBender" /sd=C:\Games\OBender            <---
"GNUChes5 xboard"
}
         


///////////////
OR CMD LINE:

   winboard.exe  /fcp obender.exe



 


